@startuml
' 时序图 - 用户登录流程

title 用户登录时序图

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam handwritten false

actor User as 用户
participant Frontend as 前端
participant Backend as 后端
participant Redis as Redis缓存
participant DB as PostgreSQL

用户 -> Frontend: 输入用户名密码
Frontend -> Backend: POST /api/auth/login
Backend -> DB: SELECT * FROM users WHERE username = ?
DB --> Backend: 用户记录
Backend -> Backend: BCrypt验证密码
alt 验证成功
    Backend -> Backend: 生成JWT Token
    Backend -> Redis: SET token:{user_id} = token (1小时过期)
    Backend --> Frontend: 200 OK { token, user }
    Frontend --> 用户: 登录成功，跳转首页
else 验证失败
    Backend --> Frontend: 401 Unauthorized { message }
    Frontend --> 用户: 显示错误信息
end

@enduml